[Whispers]
Holy shit.

36:15.598 --> 36:18.032
I'm just... I'm...

36:18.100 --> 36:19.499
[Gasps]

36:23.105 --> 36:26.597
I told you not to touch anything.

36:26.675 --> 36:29.906
You don't have to pay me.
I just have to get the money... [Gasps]

36:29.979 --> 36:31.970
You're not going anywhere, Sister.

36:32.047 --> 36:36.746
Now, pick those up and go lie on the bed.

36:40.623 --> 36:42.022
No!

36:42.958 --> 36:45.051
- I told you...
- [Whimpers]

36:45.127 --> 36:47.027
To lie on the bed.

36:53.802 --> 36:55.861
Did you take off your panties
like I asked you?

36:59.375 --> 37:00.364
Slowly.

37:02.711 --> 37:04.576
Show me your mossy bank.

37:07.316 --> 37:08.408
Slowly.

37:14.156 --> 37:15.885
[Whimpers]

37:21.630 --> 37:23.495
- No!
- [Biting]

37:23.565 --> 37:26.363
[Grunts, Groans]

37:26.435 --> 37:28.164
[Screams]

37:29.638 --> 37:31.902
[Groans]

37:44.086 --> 37:47.112
- [Indistinct]
- [Mrs. Potter Crying]

37:48.757 --> 37:50.850
[Shrieks]

37:52.094 --> 37:56.258
[Sobbing, Wailing]

37:56.332 --> 37:57.924
Shh, shh, shh.

37:59.034 --> 38:00.865
No!

38:29.298 --> 38:31.061
- [Inhales Sharply]
- Oh.

38:31.133 --> 38:34.364
I'm so sorry, Sister.
I didn't mean to frighten you.

38:34.436 --> 38:36.301
I was only trying to protect your modesty.

38:36.372 --> 38:41.833
No. You could never frighten me, Doctor.
You make me feel safe.

38:43.345 --> 38:45.939
I heard about your f-fainting spell.

38:47.383 --> 38:49.681
- I wish I could have been there.
- I did ask for you.

38:49.752 --> 38:51.515
But I know how busy you are...

38:51.587 --> 38:53.248
saving lives.

38:53.322 --> 38:55.085
Yes.

38:55.157 --> 38:58.923
Well, I'm here now,
with strict instructions...

38:58.994 --> 39:01.326
rest and relaxation.

39:05.401 --> 39:07.301
But what about the creatures?

39:12.941 --> 39:16.069
Forgive me. It's a bit disconcerting
to see you out of costume.

39:16.145 --> 39:17.840
Oh.

39:17.913 --> 39:19.608
I'm sorry, Doctor.

39:21.450 --> 39:24.044
I would hate to distract you
from the important work of the day.

39:24.119 --> 39:26.178
[Chuckles]
Don't be silly.

39:26.255 --> 39:30.157
To me, the human body is nothing more
than a complex machine.

39:31.326 --> 39:36.127
Like a clock, full of...
cogs and sprockets.

39:37.733 --> 39:40.566
Now, uh, you try to get some rest.

39:40.636 --> 39:43.070
I'll check back
with the nurse in a few hours.

39:59.822 --> 40:02.256
[Woman Screaming, Faint]

40:11.433 --> 40:12.923
Are you going to cane me?

40:13.001 --> 40:14.969
If so, can we get on with it?

40:15.037 --> 40:16.527
Now, why would I cane you?

40:16.605 --> 40:18.334
I've learned to assume the worst.

40:18.407 --> 40:21.001
[Sighs]

40:21.076 --> 40:23.601
It was a long night for all of us...

40:23.679 --> 40:26.739
a lesson in the power of Satan.

40:28.383 --> 40:30.715
One can never let one's guard down.

40:34.423 --> 40:38.223
Until last night, I considered you
a corrupt little opportunist.

40:38.293 --> 40:41.729
But God always surprises me.

40:41.797 --> 40:44.391
I know what it took
for you to call the orderlies.

40:44.466 --> 40:47.162
Couldn't have been easy,
but you did it anyway...

40:47.236 --> 40:49.466
and for that, you deserve
something special.

40:51.440 --> 40:54.876
Open the door. Go ahead.

40:54.943 --> 40:56.934
Open the door and see your treat.

41:05.187 --> 41:07.155
Bring 'em in.

41:16.899 --> 41:21.427
These two didn't show your courage
and wisdom and, as such, will be punished.

41:21.503 --> 41:24.336
Your reward is... you will not.

41:25.607 --> 41:27.302
You're so twisted.

41:27.376 --> 41:30.470
Don't make me change my mind,
Miss Lana Banana.

41:30.546 --> 41:35.506
Which of these would you like to see
on our Grace's bare behind...

41:35.584 --> 41:40.749
and which one on our doe-eyed
James Dean copycat?

41:40.822 --> 41:42.813
Go ahead. Pick one.

41:45.594 --> 41:48.154
Oh, come on, Miss Winters.
Live large.

42:02.711 --> 42:04.201
I'm so sorry, Grace.

42:04.279 --> 42:05.940
Screw you, Judas bitch.

42:09.451 --> 42:11.783
Stand up, Grace. Stand up.

42:13.956 --> 42:17.915
I'm the guilty one here,
Sister. She was a pawn.

42:17.993 --> 42:21.156
She's not the one who deserves
to be punished. I am.

42:21.230 --> 42:23.630
She was just trying to help a friend,
a desperate friend.

42:25.067 --> 42:27.501
He seems to think...

42:27.569 --> 42:32.836
you're just one big scoop
of melting strawberry ice cream.

42:32.908 --> 42:35.502
[Chuckles]
Go stand over there.

42:38.447 --> 42:42.281
So that was 20 lashes each.

42:42.351 --> 42:46.082
So that makes 40 for you, Sir Galahad.

43:00.669 --> 43:02.762
- [Cane Strikes]
- [Grunts]

43:12.381 --> 43:13.871
[Loud Strike]
